io.github.u004.steamid.utils

Class USteamInvite

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.u004.steamid.utils.USteamInvite

  • public final class USteamInvite
extends Object
    A Steam invite utility.

    USteamInvite is the utility class to make conversions between SteamId's xuid and Steam invite code.

    Since:
    0.1.0

    • Method Detail

      • toCode

        public static io.vavr.control.Try<String> toCode(Long xuid)
        Convert unique Steam account identifier to the Steam invite code.

        Converts unique account identifier to hex string and replaces characters using two bases in order - and . Then places if the length of the resulting code is greater than three.

        Possible failure exceptions:

        • IllegalArgumentException
        • InvalidSteamInviteCodeStateException 
        
     // Try.failure(new IllegalArgumentException())
     USteamInvite.toCode(0);

     // Try.failure(new IllegalArgumentException())
     USteamInvite.toCode(Long.MAX_VALUE);

     // Try.success("c")
     USteamInvite.toCode(1);

     // Try.success("gqkj-gkbr")
     USteamInvite.toCode(1266042636);
        Parameters:
        xuid - SteamId's xuid
        Returns:
        Steam invite code that wrapped in Try

      • fromCode

        public static io.vavr.control.Try<Long> fromCode(String code)
        Convert Steam invite code to the unique Steam account identifier.

        Removes and replaces characters using two bases in order - and . Then parses the resulting code to an unsigned 64-bit integer.

        Possible failure exceptions:

        • IllegalArgumentException 
        
     // Try.failure(new IllegalArgumentException())
     USteamInvite.fromCode(null);

     // Try.failure(new IllegalArgumentException())
     USteamInvite.fromCode("");

     // Try.success(1)
     USteamInvite.fromCode("c");

     // Try.success(1)
     USteamInvite.fromCode("  c  ");

     // Try.success(1266042636)
     USteamInvite.fromCode("gqkj-gkbr");
        Parameters:
        code - Steam invite code
        Returns:
        SteamId's xuid that wrapped in Try

      • toCodeRaw

        public static String toCodeRaw(Long xuid)
        Rawly convert unique Steam account identifier to the Steam invite code.

        Converts unique account identifier to hex string and replaces characters using two bases in order - and . Then places if the length of the resulting code is greater than three. 

        
     // null
     USteamInvite.toCodeRaw(0);

     // null
     USteamInvite.toCodeRaw(Long.MAX_VALUE);

     // "c"
     USteamInvite.toCodeRaw(1);

     // "gqkj-gkbr"
     USteamInvite.toCodeRaw(1266042636);
        Parameters:
        xuid - SteamId's xuid
        Returns:
        Steam invite code or null

      • fromCodeRaw

        public static Long fromCodeRaw(String code)
        Rawly convert Steam invite code to the unique Steam account identifier.

        Removes and replaces characters using two bases in order - and . Then parses the resulting code to an unsigned 64-bit integer. 

        
     // null
     USteamInvite.fromCodeRaw(null);

     // null
     USteamInvite.fromCodeRaw("");

     // 1
     USteamInvite.fromCodeRaw("c");

     // 1
     USteamInvite.fromCodeRaw("  c  ");

     // 1266042636
     USteamInvite.fromCodeRaw("gqkj-gkbr");
        Parameters:
        code - Steam invite code
        Returns:
        SteamId's xuid or null
